rComments: Fair marker, incredibly approachable, and happy to help! Would certainly recommend any class with her.

An amazing instructor that makes a seemingly boring and difficult topic of archival studies really interesting and manageable to learn about. As a bonus, there were class trips to local archival institutions and was generally a fun class to take. Hands down would take any other class she instructed in the future.

This woman is adorable. She's just a tad boring a drags on a little. However, she explains things really well and gives great examples. I feel really bad when she asks the class a question and no one wants to answer. She hands you participation marks via class blog. Wouldn't suggest taking her class at night or the morning. You might fall asleep.
